-- MOVES-Investec appoints Simon Brazier portfolio manager of UK Alpha Fund 
-- By Avik Das in Bangalore
-- Mon Oct 27, 2014 10:31AM EDT
-- None



Oct 27 (Reuters) - Investec Asset Management said Simon Brazier will be appointed portfolio manager of the Investec UK Alpha Fund upon arrival in November 2014.

Investec Asset Management said the appointment is subject to approval from Financial Conduct Authority, Britain's financial regulator.